[I am not sure what is meant by "social promiscuity", but when people are in close quarters, measles virus spreads rapidly. If individuals know they are infected, they should isolate themselves to prevent others with whom they would have come in contact from getting infected. Not do so could be considered socially irresponsible, or promiscuous. - Mod.LK]

